  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Alloy</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/32px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Alloy</b> is a resource exclusive to the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC. It is obtained by refining <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Iron_Ore\" title=\"Iron Ore\">Iron Ore</a> in a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Smelter\" title=\"Smelter\">Smelter</a> and is required for several <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a> recipes. There is a 16.67% chance to spawn a single Alloy in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Secret_Bandit_Camp\" title=\"Secret Bandit Camp\">Secret Bandit Camp</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Science\" title=\"Icon Science\"><img alt=\"Icon Science.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Science.png/32px-Icon_Science.png?63b6ec\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Iron_Ore\" title=\"Iron Ore\"><img alt=\"Iron Ore.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Iron_Ore.png?8b281f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Smelter\" title=\"Smelter\"><img alt=\"Smelter.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Smelter.png/42px-Smelter.png?c99738\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Alloy\" title=\"Alloy\"><img alt=\"Alloy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Alloy.png?15755a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Alloy\" title=\"Alloy\"><img alt=\"Alloy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Alloy.png?15755a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>6</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blue_Gem\" title=\"Blue Gem\"><img alt=\"Blue Gem.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Blue_Gem.png?51fe73\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Alchemy_Engine\" title=\"Alchemy Engine\"><img alt=\"Alchemy Engine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Alchemy_Engine.png/42px-Alchemy_Engine.png?937c5f\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sprinkler\" title=\"Sprinkler\"><img alt=\"Sprinkler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sprinkler.png?d3dfff\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Alloy\" title=\"Alloy\"><img alt=\"Alloy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Alloy.png?15755a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve