  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Hamlet}}\n{{Item Infobox\n|foodType =[[Elemental]] [[File:Elemental.png|32px|link=Elemental]]<br>(non-survivor food)\n|hpRestored = 10\n|hungerRestored = 2\n|sanityRestored = 0\n|stack=20\n|droppedBy = {{Pic|32|Secret Bandit Camp}} (16.67%)\n|spawnCode=\"alloy\"}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson=Ahoy there, alloy!\n|willow=Fire makes everything better.\n|wolfgang=Fire make it strong like Wolfgang.\n|wendy=Cold and hard, like my existence.\n|wx78=PRECIOUS METAL\n|wickerbottom=Iron that has gone through metallic bonding.\n|woodie=It's like a wood block made out of metal.\n|maxwell=Durable.\n|wagstaff=Ah, refined metal. As good as any factory could produce.\n|wigfrid=A metal wörthy öf the Söns öf Ivaldi.\n|webber=Gosh. That's a lot of metal.\n|walani=Hope this is worth all the trouble.\n|warly=Metal cooked well done.\n|woodlegs=Ahoy, alloy!\n|wilba=IS'T BLOCK O' HARD METALS\n|wormwood=Bar of Clink Rock\n|wheeler=Heavy metal made heavier.\n|choose=woodlegs}}\n'''Alloy''' is a resource exclusive to the ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC. It is obtained by refining [[Iron Ore]] in a [[Smelter]] and is required for several [[Crafting]] recipes. There is a 16.67% chance to spawn a single Alloy in the [[Secret Bandit Camp]].\n\n== {{pic|32|Icon Science}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Iron Ore\n|result=Alloy\n|tool=Smelter\n|count1 = 4}}\n\n== {{Pic32|Icon Tools}} Usage ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Alloy\n|count1=2\n|item2=Ice\n|count2=6\n|item3=Blue Gem\n|count3=1\n|result=Sprinkler\n|tool=Alchemy Engine}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Alloy\n|count1=2\n|item2=Electrical Doodad\n|count2=2\n|item3=Gears\n|count3=1\n|result=Oscillating Fan\n|tool=Alchemy Engine}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Alloy\n|count1=1\n|item2=Twigs\n|count2=2\n|result=Halberd\n|tool=Alchemy Engine}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Alloy\n|count1=3\n|item2=Cork\n|count2=3\n|result=Fancy Helmet\n|tool=Science Machine}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Alloy\n|count1=3\n|item2=Hammer\n|count2=1\n|result=Tin Suit\n|tool=Science Machine}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Alloy\n|count1=1\n|item3=Lantern\n|count3=1\n|item2=Electrical Doodad\n|count2=1\n|result=Lamp Post\n|tool=Key to the City}}\n\n\n\n{{Resources}}\n[[vi:Alloy]]"
